  - I'll be watching your back in this little maze of ours. Just a friendly face
    to help you survive the dark, mate.
  - We'll get to the real tests soon enough. For now, just head through the path
    on your right and I'll meet you in the next room. Off you go... heh heh heh.
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1932431552}
  Yes: {fileID: 512094613}
  tutorial: 1
